HEADWORD: lowan
<hw>lowan</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The Australian moundbird (<spn>Leipoa
ocellata</spn>); it incubates eggs naturally in sandy mounds.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mallee fowl, mallee-fowl, leipoa, <spn>Leipoa
ocellata</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
